item.title: Fairbanks Dev Meet-up
item.description: Fairbanks developers are looking to get together to form a dev/programmer meetup in Fairbanks and form a bit of a community around that. The group is not yet sure what it’ll become - could a web dev meetup, a linux meetup, an AI group, whatever- depending on interest and skills. Time is TBD: (fill out doodle poll below to help select a time) Location is at the Fairbanks Attently.io offices (details coming with date selection).

item.title: First Fairbanks Raspberry Jam
item.description: The first Fairbanks Raspberry Jam is 1:30-3:30 p.m. on Saturday April 29th, 2017 in Downtown Fairbanks at the Fairbanks Economic Development Corporation. Join us and meet other local Raspberry Pi enthusiasts. Share your projects Find out what others are doing Learn new stuff Collaborate with others Sign up and be eligible to win a Pi at the event (must be present to win). Saturday, April, 29th 2017 1:30 - 3:30 p.
